Summary: Hovering object over tree tops stationary for atleast 30 min.
divs: Sighting DetailsI walked outside on porch about 9:32 pm and noticed I was looking west and noticed just south of west an object hovering over the tree tops at least 500 ft.It looked to glow with one red light.It was cloudy and no stars out.It appeared to move forward towards me hover and stop.I walked inside and went to bed.
